title: Spider-Man Mega Collection - Part 01 (of 04) (- Nem -)
description:
This Spider-Man collection will come in 4 (maybe 5) parts and has about everything that could be located that`s of any importance to the fan/collector of the Spider-Man comics - it will include all Series and Spin-off series (Spider-Girl/Woman) Venom, Scarlet Spider, etc) plus one-shots, mini-series, specials, giveaway, hell . . they even put Spidey on toilet paper (poor guy).
I`m sure the completests among you will be able to point to an issue here or a toothpaste giveaway there that`s been overlooked - but hopefully i`ll be able to send the Ninjas round before you get to the keyboard - seriously though - anything major overlooked let me know.

Digital issues have been used whenever available.

Important - read the .txt file


I had to remove - Web of Spider-Man (v1-v2+Ex) from this collection so I could upload this to TPB - It has not been forgotten and will be included in a later part to this collection - Thankyou. Nem.
